{"tid":2247872,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企有隻曱甴匿埋係冷氣機度可以點算","createTime":"2020-10-18T07:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T14:15:07.000Z","uid":367849,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7a71cc7e99721ec568db982f214bf9c60744d39f","tid":2247872,"uid":367849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T07:47:28.000Z","msg":"話說前晚返到屋企諗住訓嘅時候就見到冷氣機度有隻曱甴，因為我張床係正冷氣機隔離，作為一個嚟遠見到曱甴都嚇到鳩縮嘅人當然唔敢係張床度訓<br />\n<br />\n第二朝一起身即刻換晒所有床單同被諗住佢應該走咗，點知琴晚訓到一半落床痾尿返嚟就見到隻曱甴係個出風口度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n叫老母去捉佢又話隻嘢係冷氣機上面唔肯打落去，試過開冷氣趕佢出嚟都唔得，究竟點先可以整佢走？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申從來冇係間房食或者飲過任何嘢，住咗咁多年第一次有曱甴係我間房出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3960ea888de20720f16b7a6eee556e8532103a0b","tid":2247872,"uid":135867,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T07:49:00.000Z","msg":"昆蟲問題一律建議搬屋"},{"pid":"33cee4538be5c06a8c5d21508ef857f48cdbfbe7","tid":2247872,"uid":367849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3960ea888de20720f16b7a6eee556e8532103a0b","tid":2247872,"uid":135867,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T07:49:00.000Z","msg":"昆蟲問題一律建議搬屋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T07:49:41.000Z","msg":"窮撚冇錢"},{"pid":"b8715a853ec1aa7c440cdce19cafb9b460919f66","tid":2247872,"uid":135867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T07:49:55.000Z","msg":"其實你第一眼見到佢就要殲滅有咩理由仲留佢喺度咁耐"},{"pid":"b6ff804a3f8bb03487e4d6a69f6cafd6cbe33c48","tid":2247872,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T07:50:01.000Z","msg":"告部冷氣襲警啦"},{"pid":"74ea00b3490447f175212554443e43d2abd47319","tid":2247872,"uid":201414,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T07:50:59.000Z","msg":"養眼鏡蛇 佢地專食曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" c